<div type="definition">
<p>SLOW IN CHANGING.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for something happening gradually rather than abruptly is jiàn 漸.</p>
<p>2. Shāo 稍 refers to something happening increasingly.</p>
        </div>
